title: El dia divertido de Falafel
description: Cuando Falafel decide empacar sus cosas e ir a la ciudad, Manzana y Cebollín deben convencerlo de quedarse.

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs/Mizzen in Action
description: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs: The girls must literally work as one to try and stop Mojo from destroying Townsville./Mizzen in Action: Captain Crack McGraigen and his crew are tossed forward in time where discover the chemical X that marks the spot and it is up to the girls and Professor to send the super-charged pirates back to their own time.

title: Kelsey Quest
description: Kelsey accepts a quest from the Elders of the Creek, but is she ready for her terrifying opponent?

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 1
description: While Windblade is away on a mission, Bee decides to relive a fun memory.

title: Off Colors
description: Steven finds some unusual new allies.

title: It Grows
description: As everyone celebrates Valentino for growing his first facial hair, a jealous Vic resorts to magical methods to grow a mustache and compete for attention.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: The Mirror
description: When Gumball refuses to forward a scare email, the curse becomes all too real. Gumball receives a scare-email from a freaky ghost and decides to ignore it, despite Darwin's advice. He refuses to admit it, but the curse starts to come true and his whole family gets dragged into another dimension. Gumball and Darwin, with help from Carrie, set out to save their family.

title: Jugo arcoiris
description: Después de desafiarse unos a otros a tomar el Latte de Pegaso de Chef, Izzy y Jude están llenos de energía y Duncan y Courtney hacen un viaje por carretera para tratar de reemplazar la bebida antes de que Chef descubra que desapareció.

title: Drilling Deep
description: At school, Aki struggles with the side effects of his newly replicated Drill Man schematics; later, as Mega Man, he learns to control his Fire Powers in thwarting Drill Man's assault on Skyraisers Inc.

title: Infinity Train Trailer
description: What is the train? Where did it come from? And most importantly: What's in the next train car? Join Tulip, One-One, and Atticus in a mind-blowing adventure on the enigmatic Infinity Train.

title: La prueba
description: Steven va a juicio.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Aspirations
description: The Gangreen Gang is actually committing brilliant crimes. But behind every great gang, there has to be a great woman.

title: Butt Dial
description: Mordecai pocket dials an embarrassing message on Margaret's phone.

title: The Krakken
description: While stopped at a lakefront campsite, Ben has a chance encounter with a Loch Ness type sea monster called a Krakken, controlled by an evil poacher.

title: Omni-Copped
description: When Grandpa Max's engineer buddy Phil Billings gifts Team Tennyson the Omni-Copter, a state of the art flying vehicle that can transport the Rustbucket for overseas adventures, Steam Smythe takes to the skies to ground Ben and company's first test flight; but unbeknownst to our heroes, Smythe was sent to battle Ben's latest alien forms by a mysterious, powerful enemy: the Forever Knight.

title: Sidekick Scouts
description: KO gets more than he bargained for when he gets a sidekick.

title: Chata's Quinta Quinceañera
description: Vic and Val want to go to a friend's pool party on the same day as their grandma's quinceañera, so they use a magical flute that allows them to teleport and attend both at the same time.

title: Secret Swapper of Doom
description: When the girls get a Paper Fortune Teller that can predict the future if they tell it a secret, they begin to rely on it to predict everything. But when it predicts the Powerpuff Girls will be destroyed, the girls must find a way to stop the future from happening.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Cluckwork Orange
description: After befriending a chicken with a bad attitude at a petting zoo, Jude is followed back to school by the chicken. He defends the bad bird's behavior until he can defend it no longer.

title: Memory Part 1
description: Windblade tries to help Bumbleebee but he is wary of this "stranger".

title: A Made Up Story
description: Someone is defacing all the posters and statues of Townsville with make-up. Can the girls stop this makeover takeover or will they get the blush off?

title: Crece
description: Mientras todo el mundo celebra a Valentino porque le creció su primer vello facial, Vic se pone celoso y recurre a métodos mágicos para dejarse crecer el bigote y competir por la atención.

title: Squirreled Domination
description: Rare food enthusiast Füd sends the Warriors on a mission to the Deepest Darkest Woods to gather five golden acorns from a golden oak tree for a golden acorn casserole, but poor Vambre has a secret fear of squirrels, and it turns out that golden squirrels are the scariest of them all!

title: The Brood
description: Craig's determination to get his granddad a cicada shell causes him, Kelsey and JP to become trapped in their stump!

title: The Bergerac
description: The Titans give Robin advice to guide him through his camp romance with Wonder Girl.

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Teletraan X Part 2
description: Investigating a signal in an abandoned missile silo, Bee and Windblade discover their computer back up drone Teletraan X, but it's a trap!

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Crossover Nexus
description: When KO finds himself trapped inside an mysterious place, he encounters other Cartoon Network Heroes and they band together to escape.

title: La cita
description: Cuando Chef está feliz ordena pizza para los niños. Esto le da a Owen & Jude la idea de crear una falsa admiradora secreta para Chef.

title: Stuck Together
description: Steven and Lars spend some time together.

title: Snot and Tears
description: Robin tells the Titans to stop being reckless teens or the Creepy Catcher will get them.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 1
description: With Windblade captured by the Seekers, Bumblebee is on his own for the first time and is responsible for saving Cybertron.

title: The Hands of Time
description: Master Wu mistakenly tries to single-handedly complete a battle he began decades ago against Acronix, one of the twin Hands of Time. But the arrival of the first Time Blade, a weapon with the power to speed up time, sends the Ninja to the Monastery just in time to rescue their master from certain doom.

title: Train on a Snake
description: Lady Hiss hires the Warriors to train her to be super tough.

title: The More Things Change Part 1
description: Now on his own, Ben sets out to be a solo superhero, with new alien heroes at his disposal, but Grandpa Max has other plans. (Introducing Rook, Malware, Khyber, Nemetrix alien Crabdozer, new Ben aliens Feedback & Blox, Pakmar.)

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Artesanias traviesas
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic libera al señor de las travesuras del interior una reliquia antigua, V y V tienen que trabajar en equipo para volver a encerrarlo.

title: Mushroom Menace
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman wants the Warriors For Hire to defend her giant pumpkin home from the dreaded Smashroom Mushroom, but Vambre and Prohyas can't complete their mission without help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword!

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: Chess Master Steve
description: Pizza Steve goes to great lengths in order to beat Mr. Gus at a game of chess.

title: Atrapados juntos
description: Steven y Lars pasan algo de tiempo juntos.

title: #FightAtTheMuseum
description: Supergirl always relies on her strength, but she'll need more than brawn to stop brainy Catwoman from stealing valuable gems from the local science museum.

title: Ventila-hala
description: Chef le confisca la mega-bola a Owen y la guarda en su oficina. Duncan, viendo una oportunidad para conseguir ayuda escapando de la guardaería, lidera un equipo de fuga por los conductos del aire acondicionado para recuperarla.

title: Whiteout Part 2
description: Windblade flies to the Himalayas to investigate while Bee watches television, acquiring new verbal "samples".

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Videodrone
description: Mega Man must stop Hypno Woman from turning the students and teachers at Silicon Central into her mindless drones.

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: The Heart
description: When Mr. Robinson accidentally let slip how little he cares for Gumball and Darwin, they react by giving him the cold shoulder.  Surprisingly Mr. Robinson misses them and tries to win back their friendship. After a few failed attempts, Gumball and Darwin realize that Mr. Robinson's heart is protecting him, so they give it an intense affection overload.

title: Show Don't Tell
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max arrive at a Native American national park to witness the Ayasha Plinths, an ancient Stonehenge-like rock formation. But when the sinister sorcerer Hex arrives, Ben must battle against a beast Hex magically made out of huge rocks!

title: Throwing Shade Part 2
description: Mega Man stops Fire Man by replicating his powers and fighting fire with fire. Unfortunately, Mega Man also learns that he can replicate a robot's mental state as well, and must get his own anger under control to win. Defeated, Fire Man reports back to his secret master, Sgt. Night!

title: Folk Art Foes
description: When Vic accidently unleashes the lord of mischief from an ancient relic, V and V have to work together to trap it back inside.

title: Hot Sauce
description: A quest for their favorite hot sauce causes the Bears to get involved with a sting operation.

title: Poles Apart
description: A trip to the South Pole goes upside down when Team Tennyson lands on the North Pole instead, but Ben quickly discovers the culprits: Solar & Polar Twain, magnetically-powered scientists who want to hold the world ransom by threatening to reverse Earth's magnetic poles!

title: This Spells Disaster
description: The gang is planning a surprise for Puppycorn, so they spell things out when talking so he won't find out. Desperate to know what they're saying, Puppycorn finds a magic book that he thinks will help him learn to spell, but unbeknownst to him, it's teaching him how to cast spells! Will Puppycorn realize that knowledge is power and some secrets are kept for a reason?

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: A Jolt from the Past
description: Alien pests from Ben's youth come back, but now they need Ben's help. (Introducing Fistrick, & new Ben alien Gravattack.)

title: Una epoca de traidores
description: Lloyd lucha con su papel como maestro en entrenamiento y Nya hace todo lo posible para reiniciar a Zane.

title: Walnuts & Rain
description: Finn & Jake stumble into two different holes and meet two different fates.

title: Dark Purple
description: Susan Strong and her allies infiltrate the mysterious Super Porp factory.

title: Project Ray Way
description: When Raymond starts his own fashion line, Rad and Drupe decide to make something even better.

title: Sabotage Part 2
description: Shockwave creates false memories designed to convince Bee he was always a Decepticon spy.

title: Una linea en la arena
description: Jay lucha por defender la casa de su familia.

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Teletraan X Part 1
description: The Decepticon Armada is nearing Earth to seek the Allspark and are desperate for clues.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Esto llega hasta el Once
description: Durante una última parada en una juguetería antes del viaje inaugural de Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max a través del Atlántico, Ben se encuentra con su antiguo bravucón, Kevin 11, que ahora tiene nuevos poderes. Es capaz de transformarse en alienígenas al igual que Ben, como el doble "pirata" de Cannonbolt: iWreckingbolt!

title: Quintos Quinces
description: Victor y Valentino quieren ir a la fiesta en la piscina de un amigo el mismo día que la fiesta de quince años de su abuela, así que usan una flauta mágica que les permite teletransportarse y asistir a ambas al mismo tiempo.

title: Rath of Con
description: Back stateside, Ben can't get into a cat cosplay competition, Top Tail, without a costume of his own; but when he goes Rath, a new cat-like alien with an attitude, Ben's newfound wild side quickly becomes much more than he bargained for.

title: Monstruos Bebes
description: Alice tienta a Oscar y a sus amigos monstruos para que asistan a un té festivo, pero el objetivo real es convertir a los monstruos en tiernos bebés.

title: You Forgot Your Floaties
description: Finn & Jake storm Magic Man's house to rescue his new apprentice.

title: I Am Jethro
description: When a different kind of Jethro rolls off the assembly line, the plaza is in for some surprises.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: No lo digas y Hazlo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max llegan a un parque nacional nativo americano para conocer los plintos de Ayasha, una antigua formación rocosa parecida a la de Stonehenge. Pero cuando llega el siniestro hechicero Hex, iBen debe luchar contra una bestia que Hex hizo mágicamente con rocas enormes!

title: Cube Part 2
description: Windblade finds it hard to believe that Bee can't remember his favorite sport, Cube!

title: The Extinction Event Part 2
description: Shockwave orders the Seekers to help him create an extinction event and destroy all organic life on the planet.

title: Tamaranian Vacation
description: Hoping to find out what makes Starfire so sweet and loving, the Titans visit her home world of Tamaran.

title: Pizza Eve
description: Uncle Grandpa falls for Pizza Steve's "girlfriend" and ends up in serious danger.

title: Sabotage Part 1
description: From his lab on Cybertron, Shockwave launches an attack on Bee's most vulnerable place...his memories.

title: Venthalla
description: Owen has his super ball confiscated and locked up in Chef's office. Duncan, seeing an opportunity to get help escaping the daycare, leads an away team into the vents to recover Owen's ball.

title: Dead Ringer
description: When Vic doesn't pick Val for his soccer team, Val vows to win with his own squad. But when his team doesn't match up, he resorts to supernatural means to win.

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: El pollo maniaco
description: Después de hacerse amigo de un pollo con mala actitud en un zoológico de contacto, este lo sigue de regreso a la escuela. Él defiende la mala conducta del ave hasta que ya no puede seguir haciéndolo.

title: Chips & Ice Cream
description: BMO's favorite entertainers unexpectedly find a new home at the tree house.

title: #ShockItToMe
description: Leslie Willis, the meanest girl in school, becomes a social media sensation by posting mean-spirited videos on her MetropoVids channel, causing Wonder Woman to question the moral integrity of the people who live in the World of Man.

title: The Journey Part 2
description: The Autobots are nearly out of Energon, so they land on a dark planet where they encounter subterranean creatures.

title: Siloed Part 1
description: Windblade is playing Cube on Cybertron with Bee when she realizes these are memories and she is still held captive by Slipstream.

title: Cube Part 1
description: Bee discovers a mysterious object in the stolen Decepticon shuttle.

title: Magical Moments: Week 4
description: This week's magical moment is...an exclusive new episode sneak peek!

title: Pool Duel
description: Unikitty and the gang are having a great time at the public pool, until they try to get Puppycorn to swim in the deep end with them. Puppycorn is terrified of the deep end. Now Unikitty and the gang must get him over his fear, so he can have maximum pool fun. Meanwhile, Master Frown and Brock are hatching a plan to ruin everyone's fun, by pulling the pool's plug.

title: Lost in Time
description: Kai and Nya stow away aboard Krux and Acronix's time traveling snake mech in a desperate attempt to save Master Wu. But when they arrive in the past, they must help the Elemental Masters prevent the Hands of Time from literally re-writing NinjaGo history. Meanwhile, the the Ninja remain in the rapidly-shifting present trying to help Kai and Nya's father, who was hit with a Time Punch.

title: Pijamas Pijamas
description: Oscar finge hablar con unos pijamas llamados "Jimjams" para hacer feliz a su amigo Pijama.

title: I See a Funny Cartoon in Your Future/Octi-Gone
description: I See a Funny Cartoon In Your Future: The girls have the rare task of fighting a medium who is committing petty thefts./Octi-gone: When Bubbles finds a single leg of Octi's, she sets out to find out who took her toy and what they want from her.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Omnicoptero
description: Cuando el ingeniero Phil Billings, amigo del Abuelo Max, le regala al equipo Tennyson el Omni-Copter, un vehículo volador de última generación que puede transportar el Rustbucket hasta aventuras en el extranjero, Vapor Smythe sube a los cielos para obligar a aterrizar el primer vuelo de prueba de Ben y su familia. Pero sin que nuestros héroes lo sepan, Smythe fue enviado a combatir las formas alienígenas más nuevas de Ben por un misterioso y poderoso enemigo: el Caballero por Siempre.

title: Plane Excited
description: Clarence is all excited visit his grandma when he learns that Chad has never been on a plane. Clarence makes it his mission to help Chad get through a hectic flight.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 1
description: With the help of Teletraan- X, Bee and Windblade excavate an deactivated Autobot that looks like a dinosaur.

title: Memory Amok
description: When Puppycorn witnesses Unikitty do the most embarrassing thing ever, he vows he will never forget it. Desperate, Unikitty uses Dr. Fox's memory machine to erase Puppycorn's memory of the embarrassing event. In the process, Unikitty accidentally releases all of Puppycorn's memories. Now she and the gang must scramble to capture all the scampering memories, or Puppycorn will forget his life.

title: Waffles
description: Cyborg and Beast Boy annoy the other Titans by refusing to say anything but "Waffles."

title: #SuperWho?
description: Overwhelmed by the amount of Superman coverage in Metropolis, Supergirl decides to get out there and really show the city what she can do. But when Superman inadvertently puts everyone in harm's way, Supergirl has to decide whether to do what's good for the people or what's good for her ego.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val le guarda rencor a Vic, lo cual atrae sin querer a un malvado cadejo, una bestia mitológica parecida a un lobo.

title: Free Chili
description: When Owen hides a walkie-talkie inside his chili dog, Harold believes it's an alien here to destroy Earth.

title: Please Rush Home
description: A misunderstanding between Mega Man and Rush ends in the robo-pup running away from home, only to be reunited and reconciled during a confrontation with Wave Man.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 2
description: Bumblebee doubts his abilities as he has to find the Ark to awaken Optimus and the Autobots.

title: Jinxed
description: Robin ignores the rules for a game of jinx and ends up losing his voice.

title: Secrets Discovered
description: Secrets are revealed as Nya confronts the Samurai X imposter, Kai pursues the truth about his parents and the other Ninja desperately seek to locate and rescue Master Wu. But as usual, some answers only lead to more questions.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: The Last Donnycorn
description: When Donny the Unicorn is hunted by a seemingly unstoppable foe, the Powerpuff Girls have to find a way to save him before it's too late!

title: Manzana esta en Problemas
description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Carroneros
description: Lloyd se da cuenta de que hacerse cargo del debilitado Maestro Wu no es una tarea fácil.

title: Convencion de Rath
description: De regreso en casa, Ben no puede inscribirse en un concurso de cosplay de gatos sin su propio disfraz. Pero cuando se convierte en Rath, un nuevo alienígena con aspecto felino y mal carácter, el lado salvaje que Ben acaba de descubrir pronto tendrá resultados inesperados.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 1
description: Bee, Windblade and Grimlock finally determine the location of the lost ship, the Ark.

title: The Limo
description: To help distract Panda from his girl problems, Grizz and Ice Bear treat him to a ride in a limo.

title: Uncle Dummy
description: Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve try to convince Mr. Gus that his ventriloquist dummy is alive.

title: The Mess
description: The boys stay up all night, even though the next day they're supposed to be babysitting Polly, Penny's little sister. They're so tired that they manage to lose Polly in the blink of an eye. They desperately look for her, but find themselves in increasingly weird situations every time they accidentally nod off.

title: The Hatching
description: The Ninja learn more about the Krux and Acronix, the two fallen Elemental Masters known as the Hands of Time, and are sure this threat has finally been eliminated. But with Wu out of action and suffering from the effects of the Time Punch, the Ninja discover a new enemy in their midst, the Vermillion Warriors. And the Ninjas have no idea who controls them.

title: La incubacion
description: Los Ninja descubren un nuevo enemigo en medio de ellos.

title: Freedom Cactus
description: Clarence draws a comic for the school paper and it becomes a huge hit with the kids. When angry parents step in and censor the comic's crass humor, Clarence must stand up for his artistic vision.

title: The Date
description: When Chef is happy he orders pizza for the kids, this gives Owen & Jude the idea to create a fake secret admirer for Chef.

title: Maccadam's Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bee's memory must be coming back - they access the Hivemind and visit three different eras of Maccadam's.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Allspark Part 2
description: They search for clues as to the whereabouts of the Allspark and uncover another important memory!

title: Scavengers
description: In the midst of an epidemic of mysterious metal thefts by the Vermillion Warriors, Lloyd realizes stepping up and taking over for the ailing Master Wu is not an easy task.

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: Hunted
description: Three alien bounty hunters are hot on Ben's trail. But one of them is a secret agent trying to make sure the Omnitrix does not fall into evil hands.

title: More Everyone's Tube
description: Through another video browsing session online, we get more videos uploaded by the Bears and their friends.

title: This One Goes to 11
description: During one last stop by a toy store before Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max's maiden voyage across the Atlantic, Ben runs into an old bully, Kevin 11, who now has new powers. He's able to transform into aliens just like Ben, such as the "bootleg" doppelgänger of Cannonbolt— Wreckingbolt!

title: Futbol a Muerte
description: Cuando Vic no elige a Val para su equipo de fútbol, Val promete ganar con su propio equipo. Pero cuando su equipo no está a la altura, recurre a medios sobrenaturales para ganar.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 2
description: Teletraan-X's scans reveal their old friend Grimlock, who is intent on finding the rest of his missing dinosaur friends.

title: Fractured Part 1
description: Windblade discovers Bumblebee in the desert on his own.

title: Roadtrip Ruckus
description: Richard has decided to take Unikitty and the gang for a pleasant and relaxing 10 hour road trip. At first everyone is against the trip, but they soon start to have fun. Unfortunately, their idea of fun is not Richard's.  He soon begins to give in to his inner road-rage. To make matters worse they are being chased by a killer semi-truck, and their car has been invaded by weird bug hitchhiker.  Will Richard loose it, or will the trip be a great success?

title: Saltar del fuego a un mar hirviente
description: Kai y Nya son chantajeados para que usen sus poderes elementales combinados para salvar al Maestro Wu que se desvanece rápidamente.

title: The Trial
description: Steven goes on trial.

title: It Was Them
description: Dr. Animo has escaped his Plumber prison, and Ben and Rook must track him down before he turns the world into his personal mutant ant farm! (Introducing Nemetrix alien Slamworm, Galvan Plumbers Blukic and Driba, Arctiguana, new Ben alien Crashhopper.)

title: Siloed Part 2
description: Windblade manages to fight her way out when Slipstream is called away and she discovers Bee and Teletraan-X are there to help!

title: Potion in the Ocean
description: Witchy Simone joins the Warriors on a mission deep in the Fickle Sea to find an eye of newt for her magic potion, but Man Fish the Fish Man won't let them harm his sea newt pal!

title: The Secret Life of Blossom Powerpuff
description: When Blossom can't join her favorite school club, she imagines what her life would be like if she joined other clubs.

title: The Great Spaghetti Western
description: Mr. Gus repeatedly runs afoul of a crooked mayor while winning the hears of the townsfolk.

title: Agua de Ensalada Caliente
description: Robin debe salvar a los Estados Unidos de una nueva invasión británica cuando beber té vuelve ingleses a los demás Titanes.

title: Hot Stretch
description: Ben and Rook encounter a race of elastic, hot-blooded aliens in Undertown who want to use a stolen nuclear fusion engine to activate a volcano! (Introducing Ester, Seebik & the Kraaho.)

title: Video Game Wizard
description: Mordecai and Rigby enter a video game tournament to win a video game controller.

title: Insignias de Choco Monedas
description: Oscar se entera de que puede ganar medallas al mérito que desbloquean premios.

title: Pausa y efecto
description: Kai se enfrenta a su padre solo para descubrir que sus padres son en realidad cautivos. Mientras tanto, los Ninja trabajan para liberar a Wu, Cyrus Borg y otros cautivos.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 2
description: Bee remembers an early version of Megatron where he was a gladiatorial hero, but realizes how dangerous he became.

title: Megatron Is My Hero Part 1
description: Windblade explains the threat of Megatron and the Decepticons to Bee.

title: Innervasion Part 2: Call the Dream Police
description: After defeating the Warbot and discovering Vilgax inside, Ben's "secret voices" only worsen and begin affecting his sleep, but once Gwen discovers a sleepwalking Ben using missing items from the campsite to create his own massive Junkbot, it is up to Ben to stop his own creation.

title: The Squashening
description: To escape a monster, the girls have to tell him a scary story.

title: The Interrogation
description: After Mr. Reese discovers his precious car smeared with meatball sauce, he pulls out his officer's cap and enlists Clarence to help his investigation to nab the culprit.

title: The Perfect Adventure
description: When Mao Mao gets hungry for the perfect adventure, Adorabat tells a white lie.

title: Eruption Part 1
description: As the Autobots discover the Ark, they have to wake up their friends in this battle for the future.

title: The Attack
description: The Ninja celebrate their escape from the Vermillion Army and their retrieval of the Emerald Time Blade but with Acronix and Krux determined to get their Blade back, the Airjitzu Temple becomes a battleground.

title: El Equipo Perfecto
description: A Cebollín le preocupa que su relación con Manzana corra peligro cuando un gato callejero entra en su vida.

title: Bonnie & Neddy
description: Finn and Jake, acting on orders from Candy Kingdom's new ruler Princess King of Ooo, stumble upon one of the kingdom's greatest secrets.

title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

title: El Primer Dia
description: Las familias de Oscar y Erizo, que son mejores amigos, los dejan en su primer día de campamento de verano.

title: Dewey Wins
description: Steven helps Mayor Dewey run a difficult campaign.

title: Mom App
description: Hoping to finally get the mom-experience, the Bears use an app that'll bring a mom right to their door.

title: Clarence and Sumo's Rexcellent Adventure
description: On a school trip to the Aberdale Natural History Museum, Clarence and Sumo check out the displays, goof around with the exhibits and even remove a tooth from the T-Rex display.

title: Bucky and the Howl
description: After Clarence learns Sumo's in the school musical, he joins up and enthusiastically promotes the show. On opening night with a packed house, stage fright takes hold of Sumo and he runs off leaving Clarence to go on alone.

title: Propinas
description: Luego de destruir por accidente el boleto de Falafel para un concierto, Manzana y Cebollín deben descubrir un modo de evitar la furia de Falafel.

title: The Journey Part 1
description: Bee accesses a memory from onboard the Ark on its journey from Cybertron to Earth.

title: Shadowstriker Part 1
description: Bee doubts his fighting abilities as he continually loses in practice to Windblade.

title: #Beeline
description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

title: Whiteout Part 1
description: Bee remembers his escape pod from the Ark crashed in the snowy Himalayas.

title: Pause and Effect
description: Kai confronts his dad for aiding the Hands of Time only to discover his parents are actually Acronix and Krux's captives. Meanwhile, as the Ninja work to free Wu, Cyrus Borg and the rest of the Hands of Time's captives, a third Time Blade arrives, one with the power to temporarily stop time!

title: The Web
description: Gumball and Darwin realize that the adult residents of Elmore are dangerously naive when it comes to being safe online. In fact they are in serious need of the boys help with even the simplest of tasks. And no more so than their mom, Nicole.

title: Washington B.C.
description: Ben must use the Omnitrix to transform into alien heroes to battle Dr. Amino and his transmorphed dinosaurs running rampant in Washington DC.

title: Saxofon vuelve a casa
description: Oscar se hace amigo de un Yeti adolescente.

title: The Password
description: Gumball and Darwin are shocked to discover that Anais is Dad's favourite child. Mom has forced Dad to install a password on the computer. The pop-up clue advises them that the password is the name of Dad's favorite child. After trying "Gumball" and "Darwin" unsuccessfully, they discover the answer is, in fact, "Anais". They are determined to become Dad's favorites by any means necessary, even if it means undermining each other, plotting against Anais or driving a wedge between mom and dad . . .

title: Allspark Part 1
description: Hiding from the Decepticons, Windblade use her Cityspeaker powers to search Bee's memory files.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val holds a grudge against Vic, unwittingly attracting an evil cadejo, a mythological wolf-like beast.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Uncle Grandpa for a Day
description: When UG gets his head stuck in a peanut butter jar, Mr. Gus and Pizza Steve have to pretend to be UG and help a kid.

title: Eruption Part 2
description: Teletraan-X has to reboot the offline computer systems to wake up their Autobot friends and the ship while fighting the Deceptions.

title: Under the Overpass
description: Craig and his friends travel to find honeysuckle in the creek but discover a whole new part of the creek.

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: A Time of Traitors
description: Kai's investigation of a Vermillion Warrior Helmet leads him to discover Krux is alive and well in NinjaGo, living under an assumed identity. Meanwhile, as the Vermillion Warriors go on a kidnapping spree, Lloyd struggles with his role as master-in-training and Nya does her best to reboot Zane, who was knocked off line in his first battle with the Vermillion.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Out of the Fire and into the Boiling Sea
description: The Hands of Time blackmail Kai and Nya into using their combined elemental powers to retrieve the fourth and final Time Blade from the Boiling Sea with the promise the siblings can use its reversal power to save the quickly-fading Master Wu. Meanwhile, the Ninja and Cyrus Borg get unexpected help from Samurai X as they attempt to destroy the Hands of Time's time-travelling snake mech before it's operational.

title: Vulture's Nest
description: Craig and his friends start a band, but Craig is haunted by a frightening nightmare.

title: Las manecillas del tiempo
description: El maestro Wu intenta completar una batalla que comenzó hace décadas contra Acronix.

title: Shadowstriker Part 2
description: Through memory, Bee is shown some of his past triumphs, like rescuing Optimus from Shadowstriker.

title: The Extinction Event Part 1
description: Decepticons Shockwave and Shadowstriker arrive on Earth with a simple plan to find the Allspark.

title: Lars' Head
description: Lars finally lets Steven in.

title: Duck Duck Juice
description: After daring each other to drink Chef's Pegasus Rainbow Latte, Izzy and Jude are jacked up like crazy and Duncan and Courtney take a road trip to try and replace the drink before Chef finds out it's gone.

title: Falafel's Fun Day
description: When Falafel decides to pack up and leave the city, Apple and Onion have to convince him to stay or they'll have to leave too.

title: Secretos revelados
description: Los secretos se revelan cuando Nya se enfrenta al impostor Samurai X, Kai persigue la verdad sobre sus padres y los otros Ninja buscan desesperadamente localizar y rescatar al Maestro Wu.

title: Think Positive
description: Pops orders Benson to stop yelling at Mordecai and Rigby.

title: Muscle Mentor
description: Rigby gets mentored by Muscle Man.

title: Skips vs. Technology
description: Skips wants to help Mordecai and Rigby with their computer problems.

title: Awaken Sleeping Giants Part 2
description: Slipstream and her Seekers engage in battle as our heroes trek towards the Ark.

title: La cabeza de Lars
description: Lars por fin deja pasar a Steven.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 2
description: Bee finds himself on Velocitron with Hod Rod to have some fun but it turns into a nightmare as the Plague of Rust descends.

title: Descoloridas
description: Steven encuentra unos nuevos aliados fuera de lo común.

title: Tooth Trouble
description: Puppycorn loses his first tooth and Unikitty's excited for her little bro, now he​ ​gets a visit from​ ​the​ ​legendary Tooth Fairy!​ ​But when the Tooth Fairy is a no-show, Unikitty and her friends take on the mantle and responsibilities. But will they play too fast and loose with loose teeth and hit a raw nerve?

title: Chile libre
description: Cuando Owen oculta un walkie talky dentro de su perro con chile, Harold cree que es un alienígena que vino a destruir la tierra.

title: Polos Opuestos
description: Un viaje al Polo Sur queda patas arriba cuando el equipo Tennyson aterriza en el Polo Norte. Pero Ben rápidamente descubre a los culpables: iSolar y Polar Twain, unos científicos con poder magnético que quieren chantajear al mundo amenazando con invertir los polos magnéticos de la Tierra!

title: Maccadam's Part 1
description: Bee and Windblade avoid an attack by Slipstream and Bee asks to go to Maccadam's!

title: Innervasion Part 1: Message in a Boxcar
description: As Team Tennyson prepares their boxcar for an upcoming race, Ben is hearing voices and is unable to go Upgrade to enhance his car, but once the race is interrupted by a mysterious Warbot, Ben must overcome the voices inside his head if he is to defeat the giant adversary.

title: Whacky Jaxxyz
description: When the hot new toy trend of Whacky Jaxxyz comes to Lakewood, KO says goodbye to his POW Cards.

title: #SheMightBeGiant
description: Karen Beecher is always getting picked on at school, but when the local mall is attacked by a monstrous supervillain called Giganta, she discovers that tiny Bumblebee might be the only one small enough to save the day.

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: Fractured Part 2
description: Windblade realizes Bumblebee does not remember her and her mission to find the Allspark is critical.

title: A Line in the Sand
description: While the Ninja fight to save MegaMonster Amusement Park, Jay struggles to defend his family's home from the Vermillion Warriors. But the arrival of the Emerald Time Blade, with its ability to slow time, leads to a desert chase as the heroes try to reach the Blade before the snakes get it!

title: Money Man
description: The Bears help Chloe present her project for a college science contest. But Chloe's rival makes things difficult.

title: Throwing Shade Part 1
description: Sgt. Night publicly criticizes Dr. Light's views on human & robot unity during a school assembly, invoking the ire of Fire Man and forcing Silicon City's newly minted hero, Mega Man, to intervene.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: The Invitation
description: Craig and his friends are invited to an exclusive tea party with delicious desserts, if they can last to the end of the party…

title: Like Water for Bimm
description: Vambre helps to get Bimm over her mission crippling fear of water.

title: El ataque
description: Los Ninja celebran su escape.

title: Of Predators and Prey Part 1
description: After a heated argument, Ben and Rook go their separate ways, giving Khyber the Huntsman his best chance to capture Ben! (Introducing Dr. Psychobos, new Nemetrix aliens Mucillator & Terroranchula; new Ben alien Ballweevil.)

title: Perdidos en el tiempo
description: Kai y Nya se escabullen en un intento desesperado por salvar al Maestro Wu.

title: Sun Scream/City of Frownsville
description: Sun Scream: The girls get the ultimate sunburn and must try to fight crime despite their UV damage./The City of Frownsville: When the tearful Lou Gubrious sets a crying ray on Townsville, the girls must find a way to stop the tears before the town is flooded.

title: Memory Part 2
description: Windlbade and Bumblebee are attacked by Decepticons and she regains his trust.

title: Bully for You/Trolling for Laughs
description: Bully for You: The AO must handle a neighborhood bully who is using his Bakugan to pick on the local kids./Trolling for Laughs: Wynton's constant practical jokes wear thin on his Bakugan Trox so the Bakugan decide to teach him a lesson.

title: Una Nueva Vida
description: Manzana y Cebollín abandonan sus hogares y se mudan a la ciudad, donde se conocen por primera vez.
